{"word":"H3576 - כָּזַב - kâzab - kaw-zab' - Fail","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">כָּזַב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâzab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-zab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fail"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பொய்யனாகு, அபத்தமானதை உரை, பொய்ச்சொல், அபத்தம் சொல், வற்று. பொய்யன், மோசம்போ, பொய்யனாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to lie, to tell a lie, to be a liar, to be found a liar, to be in vain, to fail"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) liar (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be proven to be lying"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to lie, to tell a lie, to tell a lie with, to deceive"},{"paragraph":"2) to disappoint, to fail"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hiphil) to make a liar, to prove to be a liar"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>lie</i> (that is, <i>deceive</i>), literally or figuratively: - fail, (be found a, make a) liar, lie, lying, be in vain."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3576 - כָּזַב - kâzab - kaw-zab'/3576\">H3576</a>, <a href=\"#/H3577 - כָּזָב - kâzâb - kaw-zawb'/3577\">H3577</a>, <a href=\"#/H3578 - כֹּזְבָא - Kôzᵉbâʼ - ko-zeb-aw'/3578\">H3578</a>, <a href=\"#/H3579 - כֹּזְבִי - Kôzᵉbîy - koz-bee'/3579\">H3579</a>, <a href=\"#/H3580 - כְּזִיב - Kᵉzîyb - kez-eeb'/3580\">H3580</a>, <a href=\"#/H391 - אַכְזָב - ʼakzâb - ak-zawb'/391\">H391</a>, <a href=\"#/H392 - אַכְזִיב - ʼAkzîyb - ak-zeeb'/392\">H392</a>"}]}